<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="utf-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1">
    <title>Intercom Generate</title>
    <script src="/scripts.js"></script>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://maxcdn.bootstrapcdn.com/bootstrap/3.3.7/css/bootstrap.min.css" integrity="sha384-BVYiiSIFeK1dGmJRAkycuHAHRg32OmUcww7on3RYdg4Va+PmSTsz/K68vbdEjh4u" crossorigin="anonymous">
    <link rel="stylesheet" type="text/css" href="/style.css"/>
    <link rel="icon" type="image/png" href="https://cl.ly/9395dd6683a1/favicon.ico">
    <style>
      .navbar-brand img {
        display: inline;
        margin-right: 10px;
      }

      .navbar {
        border-radius: 0px;
      }

      .container{
        max-width: 750px;
      }

      p{
        margin-bottom: 10px;
      }
  </style>

  </head>

  <body>
    <nav class="navbar navbar-inverse">
      <div class="container">
          <p><a class="navbar-brand" href="/" ><img src="https://downloads.intercomcdn.com/i/o/71995579/7e8e462dee5d13c376ab8aa1/logo.png"> | 🏭 Generate</a></p>
      </div>
    </nav>
    <div class="container" id="intro">
      <iframe style="margin-bottom:10px" width="753" height="419" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/6QHRwibb8h0" frameborder="0" allow="autoplay; encrypted-media" allowfullscreen></iframe>

      <p>☝️ Intro + Instructions on how to get your access token. Reach out to <strong><a style="text-decoration:none" href="https://downloads.intercomcdn.com/i/o/72003015/3ca6c3cd4149460cff954dd5/awesome.gif" target="_blank">@chris</a></strong> on Slack if you run into problems or have feedback. Here's some links to help get your access token!
        <ul>
          <li>Find Your Token <a href="https://app.intercom.io/a/apps/_/developer-hub">here</a></li>
          <li>Confirm Your Installation <a href="https://app.intercom.com/a/apps/_/settings/web">here</a>.</li>
        </ul>
    </div>
    <hr>
    <div class="container">
      <form method="POST" action="/seed">
          <div class="form-group">
            <h2>Generate Users</h2>
            <input type="text" class="form-control" name="pat" placeholder="Personal Access Token">
          </div>
        <button type="submit" class="btn btn-success">Generate 30 Users 🥁</button>
      </form>
    <hr>
    </div>
    <div class="container">
      <h2>Generate Conversations</h2>
      <form method="POST" action="/conversations">
          <div class="form-group">
            <div class="alert alert-info" role="alert">
              <strong>Heads up!</strong> Make sure you have already generated some users before trying to create conversations! :)
            </div>
            <label>Personal Access Token:</label>
            <input type="text" class="form-control" name="pat" placeholder="Personal Access Token">
          </div>
          <div class="btn-group" data-toggle="button">
            <label class="btn btn-primary active">
              <input type="radio" name="role" id="CSR_button" value="CSR" autocomplete="off"> Question Set #1
            </label>
            <label class="btn btn-primary">
              <input type="radio" name="role" id="CSE_button" value="CSE" autocomplete="off"> Question Set #2
            </label>
            <label class="btn btn-primary">
              <input type="radio" name="role" id="CSL_button" value="CSL" autocomplete="off"> Question Set #3
            </label>
          </div>
        <button type="submit" class="btn btn-success">Generate! 🗣</button>
      </form>
      <hr>
    </div>

    <div class="container">
      <form method="POST" action="/seed">
          <div class="form-group">
            <h2>Boot Your Messenger </h2>
            <p>You can use this tool to boot the messenger as a User or Lead.</p>
            <p><a href="https://cs-map-spa.herokuapp.com/index.html"><button type="button" class="btn btn-primary btn-sm">Boot Messenger</button></a></p>
          </div>
      </form>
    <hr>
    </div>

    <div class="container">
      <!-- Example row of columns -->
      <footer>
      </footer>
    </div> <!-- /container -->
  </body>
</html>
